This paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB) sub-category as it provides an overview of RDF data management systems. It may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories as RDF is used for the semantic web and data exchange, which are related to these fields. Additionally, the paper may be relevant to the digital libraries (cs.DL) sub-category as RDF is used for metadata in digital libraries. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category as it discusses systems for managing RDF data.
